why did everyne become so fake? i mean, not EVERYONE is, but most ppl are. maybe they always were and im juss realizing it. but then how could i have been so happy before? why cant i be happy now?

i guess its juss ludacris to think that i could leave and then come back and things would be all better again, juss like they were when i left.  but i guess you've died. or at least who you were has. But why, then, do i hang on like theres still something there? maybe cuz i see something there... a light thats been left on in your eyes.  but did you leave this light for me to find my way back to you? or was it juss an accident? or maybe im seeing things... juss imagining what i want to see? i need answers but im scared to ask the questions becuz im scared of the real answers. i've played the scenario over and over in my head and i can juss imagine how wonderful things were and it would be so easy to juss go back to that.

but then i realize im dreaming, becuz you arent there. and the only reason i can think of is that u juss dont care anymore. maybe i killed what we had... if thats true then lock me up and gimme the death penalty, cuz i deserve it. cuz i woulda killed one of the best, most amazing, incredible people i've ever met. i wanna go back to when things were heavenly, a "utopia" of "euphoric" feelings. the first note you ever wrote me u said i gave that to you. 

now im begging to be able to give that again. 

"Brenna, I love you, and the day that my love for you diminishes, will be the day that the universe stops existing... "

looks like the universe juss stopped existing... 

why dont i feel like laughing ever again...? oh yea, becuz you said that was the first thing you ever noticed about e, the thing that u love the most.


theres a light in your eyes
thats too bright to see 
and a pain in my heart 
where you used to be 
was i wrong to assume 
you were waiting for me? 
theres a light in your eyes
did you leave that light burning for me?

i know that lately its seemed like i dont care about you. but that isnt true, baby. i still love you. im sorry you dont feel like i ever wanna hang out anymore, and i really would ask you to hang out more if i didnt feel like you have no time for me, either. i know u work alot and your school work is super important to you cuz your so studious and u wanna get straight a's and whatever, and i juss dont wanna mess that up for you. i dunno i've been missing you alot more then i really let on. come back baby. come back to me.


i miss you sweetie.... and i would love it if you stopped by tonite. juss remember, i love you cheeta!!
